Discovering LeBron James ‘King’s Pride’ Exquisite Tropical Lamborghini Aventador Roadster

Basketball Andree · 25/08/2023

﻿Nike’s 1111 Experience event in Miami last week featured this unique Lamborghini Aventador Roadster inspired by ‘King’s Pride’ LeBron XI.

The 700 horsepower monster was inspired by the recently released ‘King’s Pride’ LeBron XI, which was covered almost entirely in a unique floral print designed by Nike and seen on the collar interior of the shoe.

The ‘King’s Pride’ Lamborghini Aventador was designed exclusively for LeBron James in collaboration with Nike by Rich B Caliente, Loulavie, and Toys for Boys Miami.
